com.sylconnexity.spring18.dbschema

Class Link

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sylconnexity.spring18.dbschema.Link

  • @Entity
public class Link
extends java.lang.Object
    A class defining the schema for Links. Links are uniquely identified by an automatically generated linkID and associated with the publisherID of a given publisher and the merchantID of a given merchant.

    Links also have an associated earnings, the amount of money earned from the link. They have a customTitle provided by the user; an originalURL of the link before it was converted to a SYL link; and a imageRedirectPermahashLink, the unique hash code associated with the link.

        publisherID - Identifier for an individual influencer
        merchantID - The merchant identifier for where the SYL Link landed
        earnings - Amount of money the influencer has earned from a SYL Link
        customTitle - The title associated with the SYL Link that the user provided
        originalURL - The original URL associated with the SYL Link that the user provided
